316
00:19:16,972 --> 00:19:19,480
So to summarize, there's a lot of interest

317
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:23,496
in integrating HWTS promotion
with other interventions.

318
00:19:24,099 --> 00:19:27,207
There may well be a better chance
at realizing health gains

319
00:19:27,207 --> 00:19:31,342
because it is easier to reach the people
