321
00:19:35,667 --> 00:19:39,588
if they're respected figures,
like teachers or health care workers.

322
00:19:40,143 --> 00:19:42,703
It's also more cost-efficient
to reach these people

323
00:19:42,703 --> 00:19:46,233
by bundling interventions
into an integrated package.

324
00:19:47,115 --> 00:19:50,917
There is suggestive evidence
and a lot of enthusiasm so far

325
00:19:50,917 --> 00:19:53,742
for integration into school programs

326
00:19:53,742 --> 00:19:58,789
but there's stronger evidence that shows
that when HWTS is integrated

327
00:19:58,789 --> 00:20:01,218
into other health initiatives,

328
00:20:01,218 --> 00:20:04,880
both objectives can have
a better chance of success.

